Pick a room and hide.The devil's coming.
The devil has chosen the room in the past 8 rounds
1. This game is a casual hide-and-seek game.
2. There are two camps in this game: the hiding party, the miners; and the capturing party, the demons. All players can only join the hiding party to play the role of miner.

3. This game will provide 8 hiding rooms in the preparation stage. During the hiding countdown, you can choose any room to hide. If the preparation phase ends and at least 20 players participate in hiding, the game will be valid for this round. If the game is invalid, the game points of all hiding players will be refunded and the next round of the game will begin.

4. If the game is valid this round, after the countdown ends, the demon will randomly capture all the miners in a certain room. If hiding players are caught, these players will lose the coins currently invested in the game. On the contrary, if the hiding player succeeds in hiding, he will share the total amount of coins invested in the game by all other captured players based on the weight of the number of coins currently invested in the game.
5. Players can only choose to stay in one room to avoid demons. After selecting a room, they can switch to different hiding rooms before the countdown ends.

6. In the preparation stage, players can increase the number of coins invested in the game. The more coins invested, the greater the dividends. The number of coins invested is not allowed to be reduced. 10% of the game coins invested by the captured hiding players will be destroyed by the system, and the rest will be shared among the surviving participants.
